    ['Plan', 'We define batching, manpower, equipment, daily targets, and acceptance criteria.'],
    ['Execute', 'Teams prepare, scan, enhance, OCR, index, and verify documents in controlled batches.'],
    ['Close', 'We reconcile batches, deliver digital output, and return or store physical records as agreed.']
  ],
